# HTML CSS Showcase

## Summary
This project was built as part of a course
[Learn Responsive Web Design] (https://www.coursera.org/learn/learn-responsive-web-design)
The course was designed to take the student to a professional level in responsive web design.

### Running the project
This project was built using DevContainers in VSCODE and allows the user to 
run an nginx webserver in the container which points to a local directory
see .devcontainer/Dockerfile to adjust the location of the local filesystem and root of the project

e.g.

'RUN ln -s /workspaces/html-css-showcase/final-project /usr/share/nginx/html'




